The '''Cor Lane''', or '''Cor Run''', was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperlane]] located in the [[Tapani sector/Legends|Tapani sector]]. The route began at the [[Barnaba system/Legends|Barnaba system]] and passed through the [[Crella system/Legends|Crella system]], [[Cor I system/Legends|Cor I system]], and [[Cor II system/Legends|Cor II system]] before reaching its terminus at the [[Cor III system/Legends|Cor III system]] in the [[Barnaba Province]]. The route was devoid of debris for the most part, allowing for quick travel between [[Star system/Legends|systems]].

